OK everybody! I found a solution to the Prima-Secunda Barycentre issue. First thing you must do is delete 'PrimaSecunda\_Properties.cfg' and 'PrimaSecunda\_Resources.cfg' located in: 

Gamedata/OtherWorlds/CercaniSystem/-CONFIGS-/

There should be 2 files you must delete.

After you have deleted the files you should open the file called 'PrimeSecunda\_SigmaBinary.cfg' with a text editor. Delete everything inside it. Copy and paste the following text into the file:

Spoiler

@Kopernicus:BEFORE[SigmaBinary]  

{  

    @Body[Secunda]  

    {  

        SigmaBinary  

        {  

            name = Prima-Secunda Barycentre  

            primaryLocked = true  

            redrawOrbit = true  

            Properties  

            {  

                description = This is the Barycentre for the Prima-Secunda system  

                selectable = true  

            }  

            Orbit  

            {  

                mode = x  

                icon = x  

                color = 0,0,1,0  

            }  

        }  

    }  

}

Save the file and run KSP. The game should now work
